# Lint & Format After Changes

After making any content change to files in this repo, run lint and Prettier before considering the task done.

- Format touched files (or the whole repo) with Prettier:

```bash
bun run format
```

- Lint and autofix:

```bash
bun run lint:fix
```

- Then verify it's clean (CI-friendly, no writes):

```bash
bun run format:check
bun run lint
```

Fix any linter/type errors you introduce. Prettier owns formatting; ESLint owns correctness only. Prefix intentionally-unused vars/args with `_`.
